# CPI (Maoist) Squad Executes Villager Acting As Police Informant In Gariaband District

Author: Alan Warsaw

Publish Time: 2023-03-12T05:12:52+00:00

Update Time: 2023-03-12T18:13:32+00:00

Images: ['[9-mm-tactical-handguns-modular-lightweight-handguns-ss-FEATURED-2-800x445.jpg](https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/9-mm-tactical-handguns-modular-lightweight-handguns-ss-FEATURED-2-800x445.jpg)']

Tags: ['Chhattisgarh', 'CPI (maoist)', 'CPI(maoist)', 'Gariaband District', 'India', 'Naxal', 'naxalites', 'naxals', 'Odisha', 'Odisha State', "People's Liberation Guerrilla Army", 'PLGA', 'police', 'Police Informant', 'Police informer', 'PPW in India', 'Udanti Area Committee of the CPI (Maoist)']

Categories: ['India', "People's War"]

<!--METADATA-->

![](Images/Redspark/2023-03-12T05-12-52-00-00/9-mm-tactical-handguns-modular-lightweight-handguns-ss-FEATURED-2-800x445.jpg)**Gariaband District, March 12, 2023:** A 30-year-old man was executed by asquad of cadres belonging to the CPI(Maoist)on suspicion of being a policeinformant in Chhattisgarh’s Gariaband district, police said on Sunday.

The incident took place in Amlipadar police station area, where a group ofMaoists entered a villager’s house in Kharipatha village, located on theborder of Chhattisgarh and Odisha, an official said.

The Maoists then forcibly took the alleged informant, identified as Ramder, toa nearby forest, he said.

The alleged informant's body was found in a forest, around 7 km away from thevillage, this morning, the official said.

A police team rushed to the spot and sent the body for post-mortemexamination, he said.

“Prima facie, it seems like the man was strangled but the exact cause of thedeath will be known after post-mortem,” the official said.

A pamphlet was recovered from the spot, in which the Udanti Area Committee ofthe CPI(Maoist)claimed that Ramder was acting as a police informant, theofficial said.

> Source : https://www.siasat.com/chhattisgarh-naxalites-kill-villager-on-> suspicion-of-being-police-informer-2545820/

News Source: [https://www.redspark.nu/en/peoples-war/cpi-maoist-squad-executes-villager-acting-as-police-informant-in-gariaband-district/](https://www.redspark.nu/en/peoples-war/cpi-maoist-squad-executes-villager-acting-as-police-informant-in-gariaband-district/)

