![](Images/Philippine Revolution Web Central/2023-03-12T96-00-00-04-00/northern-samar-armed-action-1024x502.jpeg )Blown by the Red fighters of the New People's Army(BHB)-Centralnegros is the operating troop of the 62nd IB in Sitio Batang-Batangan, Barangaybucalan, Canlaon City, Negros Oriental on March 6. One was killed and one of the wounded soldiers in a harassment operation.

