# Strikes by drivers and bus conductors, continues

Author: Philippine Revolution Web Central

Publish Time: 2023-03-12T98:00:00-04:00

Modified Time: None

Description: Admiral Transport Inc. bus drivers and bus conductors are in the second week of strike. at the company garage in Quezon City. Company buses are traveling along the EDSA carousel route. Iki

Images: ['[Admiral-Transport-Workers-Union-Welga.jpg](https://philippinerevolution.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Admiral-Transport-Workers-Union-Welga.jpg)']

Categories: ["People's Struggles", 'Workers']

Type: article

<!--METADATA-->

![](Images/Philippine Revolution Web Central/2023-03-12T98-00-00-04-00/Admiral-Transport-Workers-Union-Welga.jpg )Transport Inc.'s drivers and bus conductors are in the second week of strike. at the company garage in Quezon City. The buses are traveling along the EDSA carousel route. The Admiral Transportworkers Union passed the strike after the Maneydsment refused the request of a wage increase and benefits to their negotiations for collectivebargaining agreement(CBA).

Ayon sa unyon, tatlong beses nang ipinagpaliban ng maneydsment ang mganakatakdang pagdinig at paghaharap nito at ng unyon. Paninindign ng ATWU nanararapat at makatarungan ang kanilang mga kahingian sa CBA. Kabilang sa mgaito ang kahingian para sa regular na pasahod, overtime pay, nightdifferential, at iba pa.

Walang regular na sahod ang mga manggagawa at kasalukuyang porsyento lamang saarawang kinikita ng kumpanya ang kanilang tinatanggap. Wala silang mgabenepisyo tulad ng overtime pay at health benefits. Gayundin, iniulat nito nanasa 16-18 oras kada araw nagtatrabaho ang mga drayber at konduktor sa loob ng3-4 na araw sa isang linggo. Karamihan sa mga drayber at konduktor ay higit 20taon nang nagtatrabaho sa kumpanya.

Panawagan din ng unyon na ibalik sa trabaho ang mga lumahok sa welga nangwalang pagganti ng kumpanya.

News Source: [https://philippinerevolution.nu/angbayan/welga-ng-mga-drayber-at-kunduktor-ng-bus-nagpapatuloy/](https://philippinerevolution.nu/angbayan/welga-ng-mga-drayber-at-kunduktor-ng-bus-nagpapatuloy/)

